{"type": "article", "id": 26613, "title": "葡萄酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130806Dw75OjpnQH4Gt8rE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>葡萄酒的酿造年份往往都会直接在包装上注明，但是不少人并不能真正理解葡萄在那一年收获究竟意味着什么。为了解决这个问题，Studio Sonda 同气象部门合作，为 Piquentum St Vital 设计的新包装暗藏了玄机：标签上分布着 12 个大小不一、被水打湿的圆圈，表现的是当年每个月的降雨量。这个讨巧的设计很直观地体现出了大自然的多样性，向更多人普及了酿造知识。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130804fJgd4Qtk6yn3MBWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130804zfGcYC9KhbteTU72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130805aFnMI7eTAv81VuGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130805c1yEudex84ZPrGTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}